Comment: Black takes wrong pawn by advancing back pawn instead of front pawn.  He could have kept a pawn on g4.  Instead he will have a pawn on row 5, further from promotion and giving me the choice of pawn position.  Now pxh5 so my pawn is further from his kink and his pawn is closer to mine.
